comment: The air-conditioned coffee shop is super close to my house so I like to come here. Sometimes it's very crowded and noisy, but sometimes there are only a few customers. The old employees are quite understanding, so I often come here. Prices are very reasonable. But milk coffee is a bit strong for people who drink coffee occasionally. Milk tea has a strong tea flavor, peach tea has large pieces, I like these two dishes the most. The flan is also very delicious.
